markdownRemark.html: This deliverable will report on the in depth information collected from the qualitative method used in this project’s primary research (focus groups) on CH management. The focus groups will map and examine (participants: CH professionals, public authorities, researchers) on the needs, challenges and practices in the CH sector conducted in Phase 2.
